==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Superstruct
<hw>Su`per*struct"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>superstructus</ets>, p. p. of <ets>superstruere</ets> to build
upon; <ets>super</ets> over + <ets>struere</ets> to build. See
<er>Super-</er>, and <er>Structure</er>.]</ety> <def>To build over or
upon another structure; to erect upon a foundation.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>This is the only proper basis on which to <qex>superstruct</qex>
first innocency and then virtue.</q> <rj><qau>Dr. H.
More.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Superstruction</ent>⟦br⟧
